rosbag filter

rosbag filter old_bag.bag new_bag.bag "topic == '/clock' or topic == '/scan' or topic == '/imu/data' or topic == '/nmea_sentence' or topic == '/telemetry_sigma/wheels_angle' or topic == '/telemetry_sigma/sensing/wheels_speed_esp'"

